nstrate the utility of MARS and Bento in two use cases: a high-throughput behavioral phenotyping study, and exploration of a novel imaging dataset. Together, MARS and Bento provide an end-to-end pipeline for behavior data extraction and analysis, in a package that is user-friendly and easily modifiable.{\textless}/p{\textgreater}},
